        <abstract>
            <p>Has seen some natives who express surprise by clapping the hand to mouth.</p>
            <p>Reports on a tribe that sells its ugliest slaves in order to maintain its uniformly fine appearance.</p> 
<p>In America in 1867 Darwinism was a <hi rend="italic">fait accompli</hi>. Asa Gray’s religious defence unnecessary after Theodore Parker and Emerson.</p> 
        </abstract>
